This is the beginning of a start-again-from-scratch .vim directory for me to use
more easily across my various machines. One more step towards independence of
any particular machine! It also allows for easy sharing of my vim config with
others.

To learn about the way I'm using pathogen and git submodules, check this link:

http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/
